OL,3,CWolves appoint Cesar Peixoto as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FWolves have appointed Cesar Peixoto as
OL,7,Ftheir new head coach to replace Rob
OL,8,FEdwards.
OL,10,FThe 46-year-old Portuguese joins the
OL,11,Fclub on a two-year contract, subject
OL,12,Fto a work permit.
OL,14,FPeixoto, who is a former Portugal
OL,15,Finternational, recently led Gil
OL,16,FVicente to sixth in the Primeira Liga
OL,17,Fin Portugal.
OL,26,@kD@QrrnD@Xrr
