OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1781556458
OL,3,CWolves appoint Cesar Peixoto as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FAs a player of more than 20 years,
OL,7,Fhe's won domestic honours in Portugal,
OL,8,Fand was part of Jose Mourinho's UEFA
OL,9,FChampions League-winning FC Porto
OL,10,Fsquad before moving into coaching.
OL,12,F"This is an amazing club"
OL,14,FHe told the Wolves website: "I'm proud
OL,15,Fto be here at this big, historic club
OL,16,Fin England. It's a big opportunity for
OL,17,Fme and I'm prepared to do everything
OL,18,Fto put Wolves where it belongs in the
OL,19,FPremier League.
OL,26,@kD@QrrtD@AOUvD@]OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1781556458
OL,3,CWolves appoint Cesar Peixoto as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,F"We have great players, but I think
OL,7,Fthe team can improve a lot with me and
OL,8,FI can improve as a technical head
OL,9,Fcoach.
OL,11,F"I want to put my identity onto the
OL,12,Fteam, build a strong identity at the
OL,13,Fclub and also help the team to grow by
OL,14,Fshowing my identity and my way of
OL,15,Fplaying.
OL,17,F"This is an amazing club, and it is
OL,18,Fimportant for me to make Wolves play
OL,19,Fin a way which reflects the fans.
OL,26,@kD@QrrnD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1781556458
OL,3,CWolves appoint Cesar Peixoto as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,F"It's a hard-working city with a lot
OL,7,Fof energy and a lot of passion, and I
OL,8,Fwant them to see a team which plays an
OL,9,Foffensive game, with good organisation
OL,10,Fand a team who play for the fans.
OL,12,F"I want the supporters to be proud of
OL,13,Four players, be proud of the way we
OL,14,Fplay and the way we fight game after
OL,15,Fgame to bring the victory, and to
OL,16,Fachieve the main aim, which is to put
OL,17,FWolves back in the Premier League."
OL,19,FIt was announced on Thursday (11 June)
OL,20,Fthat Wolves had sacked Rob Edwards
OL,21,Fafter just seven months in charge.
OL,26,@kD@QrrtD@AOUyD@cO]
