CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1781556458
OL,3,CWolves appoint Cesar Peixoto as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FEdwards only recorded three league
OL,7,Fwins in 27 matches as boss, during a
OL,8,Fcampaign that saw Wolves relegated to
OL,9,Fthe Championship after eight years in
OL,10,Fthe top flight.
OL,12,FThe sacking comes just days after the
OL,13,Fclub confirmed the signings of former
OL,14,FEngland international Kieran Trippier,
OL,15,Fand former Wolves striker Raul Jimenez.
OL,26,@kD@QrrwD@]rzwD@crr
