OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1781556458
OL,3,CWolves appoint Cesar Peixoto as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FPeixoto will be Wolves' fourth
OL,7,Fpermanent Portuguese head coach in the
OL,8,Flast nine years. This follows the
OL,9,Fappointments of Nuno Espirito Santo in
OL,10,F2017, Bruno Lage in 2021 and Vitor
OL,11,FPereira in 2024.
OL,13,FWolves will be playing the
OL,14,FChampionship next season for the first
OL,15,Ftime since earning promotion from the
OL,16,Fdivision in 2018.
OL,26,@kD@QrrqD@YrtrD@_rt
